title: MBMBaM 306: Face 2 Face: Foggy Bottoms
description: Here's a live performance from The Lincoln Theatre, in beautiful, humid Washington D.C.! Join us for a lengthy discussion on soupy gooses, a perplexing audience question about random acts of tap shoes and, of course, the live debut of MUNCH SQUAD.
author: shows@mbmbam.com (Justin McElroy)
